      "content": "it's not just a coincidence though. i've been tracking other things too. colors seem slightly desaturated in certain areas and sometimes the people around me repeat the same exact phrases like they're running on a loop. if this is just \"synchronicity,\" why does it feel so mechanical? like the system is struggling to keep up with all of us.",
